From aa941534050b5869a09f186e1f32e9d76deec858 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: mixelpixx <chris_stockslager@comcast.net>
Date: Sat, 28 Feb 2026 22:30:17 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] Add MCP settings tab and modernize UI/UX

MCP Settings Integration:
- Add dedicated MCP tab to File > Preferences dialog
- Enable/disable MCP server, auto-connect, port, log level, tool mode
- Display connection URL for easy Claude Code configuration
- Settings persist via Theia preference system

UI/UX Modernization:
- Add CSS design system with spacing, radius, shadow, transition tokens
- Buttons: subtle shadows, hover lift effect, modern border radius
- Toolbar: scale animations on hover, polished button states
- Dialogs: entry animation (fade + scale), visual separators
- Board selector: rounded dropdown, accent border on hover/selection
- Progress bars: gradient fill with shimmer animation
- Input fields: focus ring with teal brand glow
- List items: hover backgrounds, title accent color
- Serial monitor: styled scrollbar, input focus states
- Status bar: board/port badges with teal background
- All styling respects light and dark themes

Documentation:
- Update README with MCP settings tab instructions
- Document UI/UX modernization features

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
